IR-2007-117, IRS Releases Discussion Draft of Redesigned Form 990 for Tax-Exempt Organizations http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0,,id=171329,00.html
IR-2007-118, IRS Reminds Tax Professionals to Register Early for Tax Forum http://www.irs.gov/newsroom/article/0,,id=171407,00.html 

